=== SPORE_COLLECTIVE ===
# id: 29
# title: The Spore Collective
# chinese_title: 孢子群落
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

The walls of this section are covered in bioluminescent fungal growth. As you enter, the spores coalesce into a rough humanoid shape and tilt what might be a head. The collective intelligence observes you, communicating through chemical signals your suit translates as simple concepts.

* [Share nutrients from your rations]
  ~ gain_radical("木")
  "木" (mù) — wood, plant, organic
* [Ask the collective about this station's history]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "问" (wèn) — to ask, to inquire
* [Collect a spore sample carefully]
  ~ gain_item("biogel_patch")
  "菌" (jūn) — fungus, bacteria
* [Burn away the growth with your torch]
  ~ damage(5)
  "烧" (shāo) — to burn
